Citigroup Sees Emerging Stocks Posting ‘Strong’ Gains Over Year

-- B y   R i c h a r d   F r o s t
-- 
2011-10-03T23:47:40Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-03/citigroup-sees-emerging-stocks-posting-strong-gains-over-year.html
Emerging-markets stocks are still
likely to post “strong” gains over the next year as
“significant” earnings downgrades are already priced in,
Citigroup Inc. said.  China’s economic growth is likely to slow, as reflected in
data releases for August, “but there is little sign of a hard
landing,” Citigroup analysts led by Geoffrey Dennis wrote in
report dated yesterday.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Richard Frost at 
 rfrost4@bloomberg.net  